methods: abstract void cursorMoved(RowSetEvent theEvent) Notifies the listener that the RowSet's cursor in theEvent.getSource has moved.
abstract void rowChanged(RowSetEvent theEvent) Notifies the listener that one of the RowSet's rows in theEvent.getSource has changed.

abstract void rowSetChanged(RowSetEvent theEvent) Notifies the listener that the RowSet's entire contents in theEvent.getSource have been updated (an example is the execution of a command which retrieves new data from the database).
